column3: Thanks for the test @MarcoFalke and thanks for investigating the issue so quickly during the meeting yesterday @jonasschnelli \nACK fade505\n
This won't trigger a rescan. It should be `self.node_args[1] + ['-rescan']`.\n`self.node_args[1].extend(['-rescan'])` results in `null`?.\n

Awesome! It is always good to have fresh eyes look on the code.

Will push a fix and then squash the commits.
